WEBVTT

00:00:03.070 --> 00:00:05.450
She's running and running up the hill!

00:00:05.450 --> 00:00:08.350
With 200 meters to go,
All Haiyu is chasing her!

00:00:07.980 --> 00:00:09.530
Go!

00:00:08.350 --> 00:00:10.040
Sounds of Earth is also moving up!

00:00:10.040 --> 00:00:12.360
But she remains in the lead! Kitasan Black!

00:00:12.360 --> 00:00:13.670
Sounds of Earth is in second!

00:00:13.670 --> 00:00:14.950
Sounds of Earth!

00:00:14.950 --> 00:00:17.320
Third place, Cheval Grand, is closing in!

00:00:17.320 --> 00:00:19.600
But in first, it's Kitasan Black!

00:00:19.600 --> 00:00:22.540
And Kitasan Black outruns them all!

00:00:28.040 --> 00:00:30.300
I did it! I won!

00:00:30.660 --> 00:00:32.300
Kita-chan!

00:00:34.160 --> 00:00:37.720
This race was truly my idea of eccitazione!

00:00:37.720 --> 00:00:39.790
Second place in a G1 race! Nice!

00:00:39.790 --> 00:00:41.140
Impressive results.

00:00:41.140 --> 00:00:43.230
It really is something.

00:00:43.230 --> 00:00:44.480
Uh, it is...

00:00:47.830 --> 00:00:51.860
Man, I've got nothing left to teach her, huh?

00:00:55.940 --> 00:00:57.200
Third place...

00:01:00.180 --> 00:01:02.500
V
e
r
x
i
n
a

00:01:00.180 --> 00:01:02.500
V
i
v
l
o
s

00:01:02.500 --> 00:01:04.280
I really did it!

00:01:04.280 --> 00:01:06.490
Yeah. That was a great job!

00:01:06.490 --> 00:01:09.200
Your third G1 win, and in
the Japan Cup, no less.

00:01:09.200 --> 00:01:12.510
It's cool that you won on
your biggest stage yet!

00:01:20.640 --> 00:01:23.330
Okay, the Arima Kinen comes next!

00:01:23.330 --> 00:01:25.550
It'll be payback for last time!

